+ * @GST_VAAPI_PROFILE_MPEG2_SIMPLE:
+ *   MPEG-2 simple profile
+ * @GST_VAAPI_PROFILE_MPEG2_MAIN:
+ *   MPEG-2 main profile
+ * @GST_VAAPI_PROFILE_MPEG2_HIGH:
+ *   MPEG-2 high profile
