+ *   MPEG-4 Part-2 simple profile
+ * @GST_VAAPI_PROFILE_MPEG4_ADVANCED_SIMPLE:
+ *   MPEG-4 Part-2 advanced simple profile
+ * @GST_VAAPI_PROFILE_MPEG4_MAIN:
+ *   MPEG-4 Part-2 main profile
+ * @GST_VAAPI_PROFILE_H263_BASELINE:
